  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\"><img alt=\"House Dayne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/95/House_Dayne.svg/50px-House_Dayne.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/95/House_Dayne.svg/75px-House_Dayne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/95/House_Dayne.svg/100px-House_Dayne.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lady</span><br />Clarisse Dayne</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\"><img alt=\"House Dayne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/95/House_Dayne.svg/50px-House_Dayne.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/95/House_Dayne.svg/75px-House_Dayne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/95/House_Dayne.svg/100px-House_Dayne.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Clarisse_Dayne_by_ophelias-lamentation.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Clarisse Dayne by ophelias-lamentation.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1a/Clarisse_Dayne_by_ophelias-lamentation.jpg/350px-Clarisse_Dayne_by_ophelias-lamentation.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1a/Clarisse_Dayne_by_ophelias-lamentation.jpg/525px-Clarisse_Dayne_by_ophelias-lamentation.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1a/Clarisse_Dayne_by_ophelias-lamentation.jpg/700px-Clarisse_Dayne_by_ophelias-lamentation.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Clarisse Dayne, by ophelias-lamentation ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Starfall\" title=\"Lord of Starfall\">Lady of Starfall</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\">House Dayne</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Sons_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Sons of the Dragon\">The Sons of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Clarisse Dayne</b> was the Lady of <a href=\"/index.php/Starfall\" title=\"Starfall\">Starfall</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\">House Dayne</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clarisse_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Clarisse was considered to be proud and beautiful.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clarisse_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When King <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a> decided to take another wife, <a href=\"/index.php/Grand_Maester\" title=\"Grand Maester\">Grand Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Benifer\" title=\"Benifer\">Benifer</a> suggested Clarisse as a possible match in the hopes of detaching <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\">House Dayne</a> and their lands from <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>. Maegor dismissed his advice, however.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clarisse_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_sons_of_the_dragon.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Sons of the Dragon.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Last known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Vorian_Dayne\" title=\"Vorian Dayne\">Vorian Dayne</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_of_Starfall\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lady of Starfall\">Lady of Starfall</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Dayne_(father_of_Edric)\" title=\"Lord Dayne (father of Edric)\">Lord Dayne</a> </b>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404194218\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.094 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.316 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 894/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12492/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7340/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1177/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1256/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.200/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.58 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  304.653      1 -total\n 92.92%  283.086      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 92.45%  281.651      1 Template:In